---
title: Beef Meatballs and Linguine with tomato spinach sauce
description: The tangy tomato sauce and al dente linguine in this dish may be delicious in their own right, but the succulent 100% Irish beef meatballs might just be the best thing about this dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R04_W49_IE_IEFB18677-2_Main_high-e501c745.jpg
